<div class="container">
  <div class="box">
    {{#if result}}
      <p class="information">You have enabled API authorization. Your API is now in <strong>private mode.</strong></p>
      <p class="information">In order to make requests to <code>{{apiName}}.200ok.app</code> you will now need to add an <code>Authorization</code> header to each request:</p>
      <pre class="lang-http"><code>Authorization: Bearer {{result}}</code></pre>
      <p class="information">If you ever forget your Authorization bearer token, you will need to disable private mode from the dashboard and re-enable it to generate a new token.</p>
    {{else}}
      <p class="information">You have disabled the API authorization for <strong>'{{apiName}}'</strong>.</p>
      <p class="information">In order to re-enable it, go to the dashboard and click <em>Enable API Authorization.</em></p>
    {{/if}}
    <div class="information">
      <i class="fas fa-arrow-circle-left"></i> <a href="/dashboard">Back to dashboard</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<script src="/javascript/prism.js"></script>